The Arch mage of Waterdeed, Arron Black Staff, once created some copies of his magical items for those under his tutleage, though long lost by many of his pupils some have been found throughout Faerun.  Highly prized by many as some of the best magical items for mages around the world, these items are never sold on any market.

(Note: Level 30+ Required)
The gauche is a light, flexible blade used in the off-hand when wielding a rapier.
This heavy wooden shield is embedded with the skulls of some unknown creature.

"Close enough!"
